28/03/2004
TIRANA, Albania -- The EU and NATO praised the progress achieved by Albania in enhancing Euro-Atlantic integration, announced the Albanian Daily News on Friday (26 March). 
Albanian Foreign Minister Kastriot Islami met with the highest-ranking NATO and EU officials earlier in the week. 
Meanwhile, US Ambassador to Tirana James Jeffrey said ties between Albania and the United States are excellent, and that reforms in Albania are steadily moving ahead. 
(Albanian Daily News - 26/03/04)
